<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport">
    <title>Delete User</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .nav-group input[type="checkbox"] { display: none; }
        .nav-group input[type="checkbox"]:checked ~ .nav-subitems { display: block; }
        .nav-group input[type="checkbox"]:checked ~ label .nav-chevron { transform: rotate(90deg); }
        .nav-subitems { display: none; }
        .nav-chevron { transition: transform 0.15s ease; display: inline-block; }
        #sidebar-toggle { display: none; }
        #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .app-shell #primary-sidebar { transform: translateX(0); }
        #sidebar-toggle:checked ~ .sidebar-overlay { display: block; }
        @keyframes shake { 0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)} 20%{transform:translateX(-6px)} 40%{transform:translateX(6px)} 60%{transform:translateX(-4px)} 80%{transform:translateX(4px)} }
        .shake { animation: shake 0.4s ease; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-100 text-slate-950 antialiased">
<input id="sidebar-toggle" type="checkbox">
<label for="sidebar-toggle" class="sidebar-overlay fixed inset-0 z-20 hidden bg-slate-900/40" aria-hidden="true"></label>
<div class="app-shell min-h-screen lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[17rem_1fr]">
    <aside id="primary-sidebar" class="fixed inset-y-0 left-0 z-30 w-64 -translate-x-full overflow-y-auto border-r border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-6 transition-transform duration-200 lg:relative lg:inset-auto lg:z-auto lg:w-auto lg:translate-x-0 lg:transition-none">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center justify-between lg:block"><a class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight" href="#">Admin</a><label for="sidebar-toggle" class="cursor-pointer rounded-md p-1 text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-100 lg:hidden" aria-label="Close menu"><svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg></label></div>
        <nav class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm font-medium lg:mt-8"><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="home.twig">Dashboard</a><div class="nav-group"><input id="nav-users" type="checkbox" checked><label for="nav-users" class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-emerald-700"><span>Users</span><span class="nav-chevron"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span></label><ul class="nav-subitems ml-3 mt-1 space-y-0.5 border-l border-slate-200 pl-3"><li><a class="block rounded-md bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-1.5 font-semibold text-emerald-700" href="users.twig">All Users</a></li><li><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="create-user.twig">New User</a></li><li><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="user-roles.twig">Roles</a></li></ul></div><a class="block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100" href="#">Settings</a></nav>
    </aside>
    <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col">
        <div class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 sm:px-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><label for="sidebar-toggle" class="cursor-pointer rounded-md p-1.5 text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-100 lg:hidden" aria-label="Open menu"><svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg></label><div><h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 sm:text-base">Delete User</h4><nav class="mt-0.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500 sm:text-sm"><a class="hover:text-slate-800" href="#">Dashboard</a><svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg><a class="hover:text-slate-800" href="users.twig">Users</a><svg class="h-3 w-3 text-slate-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg><span class="text-red-600">Delete</span></nav></div></div></div>
        <div class="flex flex-1 p-4 sm:p-6">
            <div class="flex min-w-0 flex-1 flex-col gap-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"><div><h1 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-2xl">Delete User</h1><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Review ownership and access before removing this account.</p></div><a href="users.twig" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 self-start rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50 sm:self-auto">Cancel</a></div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-red-200 bg-red-50 p-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 001.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 001.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 00-3.42 0z"/></svg><div><p class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-800">This action cannot be undone.</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-red-700">Deleting Jane Smith removes login access and profile data. Reassign content before continuing.</p></div></div></div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 xl:grid-cols-[1fr_20rem]">
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-3"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">User Being Deleted</h5></div><dl class="divide-y divide-slate-100 px-5 py-2 text-sm"><div class="flex items-center justify-between py-2.5"><dt class="text-slate-500">Name</dt><dd class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Jane Smith</dd></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between py-2.5"><dt class="text-slate-500">Email</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">jane@example.com</dd></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between py-2.5"><dt class="text-slate-500">Roles</dt><dd class="text-slate-700">Administrator, Editor</dd></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between py-2.5"><dt class="text-slate-500">Articles</dt><dd class="font-semibold text-slate-900">36</dd></div></dl></div>
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-5 py-3"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">Content Reassignment</h5></div><div class="space-y-4 px-5 py-5"><label class="flex items-start gap-3"><input type="radio" name="content_action" value="reassign" checked class="mt-0.5 border-slate-300 text-emerald-600 focus:ring-emerald-500"><span class="text-sm text-slate-700"><span class="font-medium">Reassign authored content</span><span class="mt-0.5 block text-xs text-slate-500">Move articles and drafts to another user.</span></span></label><select class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:border-emerald-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500/20"><option>Morgan Lee</option><option>Avery Stone</option><option>Riley Chen</option></select><label class="flex items-start gap-3"><input type="radio" name="content_action" value="delete" class="mt-0.5 border-slate-300 text-red-600 focus:ring-red-500"><span class="text-sm text-slate-700"><span class="font-medium text-red-700">Delete user-owned drafts</span><span class="mt-0.5 block text-xs text-slate-500">Published content remains assigned to system.</span></span></label></div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-red-200 bg-white shadow-sm"><div class="border-b border-red-100 bg-red-50 px-5 py-3"><h5 class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-800">Confirm Deletion</h5></div><form id="delete-form" method="POST" action="#" class="px-5 py-5"><input type="hidden" name="_method" value="DELETE"><div class="mb-4 rounded-md bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-slate-700">Type <strong>Jane Smith</strong> to confirm deletion.</div><label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700" for="confirm_name">Confirmation</label><input class="w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:border-red-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/20" id="confirm_name" name="confirm_name" type="text" placeholder="Jane Smith" autocomplete="off"><p id="confirm-error" class="mt-1 hidden text-xs text-red-600">Name does not match. Type "Jane Smith" exactly.</p><button id="delete-btn" type="submit" class="mt-5 w-full rounded-md bg-red-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50" disabled>Permanently Delete User</button><a href="edit-user.twig" class="mt-2 block w-full rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50">Back to Edit</a></form></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer class="mt-auto border-t border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 sm:px-6"><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"><p class="text-xs text-slate-400">&copy; 2026 Admin &mdash; All rights reserved.</p><nav class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-400"><a class="hover:text-slate-600" href="#">Documentation</a><a class="hover:text-slate-600" href="#">Support</a><a class="hover:text-slate-600" href="#">Privacy</a><span class="text-slate-300">|</span><span>v1.0.0</span></nav></div></footer>
    </div>
</div>
<script>
(function () {
    var required = 'Jane Smith';
    var input = document.getElementById('confirm_name');
    var button = document.getElementById('delete-btn');
    var error = document.getElementById('confirm-error');
    input.addEventListener('input', function () {
        var match = input.value === required;
        button.disabled = !match;
        error.classList.toggle('hidden', match || input.value === '');
    });
    document.getElementById('delete-form').addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
        if (input.value !== required) {
            e.preventDefault();
            input.classList.add('shake', 'border-red-400');
            input.addEventListener('animationend', function () { input.classList.remove('shake'); }, { once: true });
        }
    });
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
